%claude:
The IPC syscalls cover several mechanisms.
[[PIPE]] creates a pipe---one of \unix's greatest inventions.
[[NOTIFY]]/[[NOTED]] handle {notes}, \plan's equivalent of
\unix signals. The [[SEG]] family ([[SEGATTACH]],
[[SEGDETACH]], etc.)\ lets processes attach shared memory
segments, similar to \unix\ [[mmap]].

