\subsection{[[pexit()]] and [[schedinit()]]}

% pexit -> sched (when up <> nil) -> schedinit
%claude:
Here is phase~2: [<pexit()>] set the state to [[Moribund]]
and called [<sched()>], which jumped to [<schedinit()>] on
the CPU's main stack. Now [<schedinit()>] finishes the
cleanup: release the MMU state, push the [[Proc]] back
onto the free list, and unlock the locks that [<pexit()>]
was holding. 
<<[[schedinit()]] switch process state cases>>=
