%claude:
When a process dies ([[Moribund]] state), [[schedinit()]]
calls [[arch_mmurelease()]] to free all its hardware page
table resources: the L2 pages are zeroed and returned to
the free page list, the L1 user entries are cleared, and
the TLB is invalidated.

