\subsection{[[ready()]]}

%claude:
[[ready()]] puts a process on the run queue at its
current priority. It is called from many places:
[[schedinit()]] (when the current process is preempted),
[[wakeup()]] (when a sleeping process's condition becomes
true), [[qunlock()]] (when a waiting process gets the
lock), [[sysrfork()]] (for the child), and [[kproc()]]
(for new kernel processes).

<<[[Procstate]] cases>>=
Ready,
