%claude:
In this chapter, I cover the remaining advanced aspects of the kernel:
floating point management, CPU caches, the memory model, SMP support
for the Raspberry Pi~2, real-time scheduling, and the 9P fileserver
protocol. These topics were deferred from earlier chapters because
